Beyond talented & out of this world. This piece deserves to be viewed by so many all over the earth. 

Itâ€™s color scheme, the figures all tell such a beautiful yet intricate story. 

A narrative that can span a variety of tales..

The attention to detail that sprouts out, this is truly art beautiful is an understatement.

Itâ€™s breathtakingly beyond all, never get tired of looking at it for every detail to feel the emotions and euphoria that shoots forth.

Itâ€™s such a twist and refreshment. 

It's nostalgic yet so telling of how fast time flies by from childhood into the greater beyond.
